---
import CourseIcon from "../../assets/courseDetail.svg";
import ReviewIcon from "../../assets/courseDetail1.svg";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Course Detail</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" /> <!-- replace with your global stylesheet -->

  <style>
    .course-detail-grid,
    .course-detail-grid h1,
    .course-detail-grid h2,
    .course-detail-grid h3,
    .course-detail-grid h4,
    .course-detail-grid h5,
    .course-detail-grid h6,
    .course-detail-grid p,
    .course-detail-grid a,
    .course-detail-grid li,
    .course-detail-grid span,
    .course-detail-grid button {
    color: white;
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Top Header already in place -->

  <!-- Banner -->
  <div class="hero-banner">
    <div>
      <h1>COURSES</h1>
    </div>
    <svg id="hero-bg-svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="499" height="247" viewBox="0 0 499 247" fill="none">
      <path opacity="0.3" d="M220.942 95.8823C249.786 89.8704 279.714 91.7797 307.532 101.406C335.35 111.033 360.012 128.015 378.885 150.539L340.993 176.342L474.028 200.809L498.6 68.9811L455.397 98.3783C420.237 53.2014 370.745 21.2521 314.992 7.73921C259.239 -5.77368 200.512 -0.0530709 148.386 23.9684C96.2607 47.9898 53.8107 88.8952 27.957 140.016C2.10342 191.136 -5.62882 249.456 6.02093 305.467L96.1444 286.299C87.4351 244.589 95.6836 201.115 119.08 165.417C142.477 129.718 179.11 104.711 220.942 95.8823Z" fill="#C4FEC7"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Course Detail Main Section -->
<main class="course-detail-grid">
  <!-- Left Content -->
  <section class="course-left">
    <CourseIcon 
    width="60" 
    height="60" 
    style="flex: none; order: 0; flex-grow: 0; margin-bottom: 16px;" 
   />
    <h2>Scrum Master Course</h2>
    <p>09/18 - 11/14</p>
    <p>Brookline, MA</p>
    <button class="register-btn">Register</button>

    <h3>ABOUT THIS COURSE</h3>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">This intensive Scrum Master course delves into the core principles and practices of the Scrum framework, providing a comprehensive understanding of the Scrum Master's role as a servant leader within an Agile environment. Through a blend of instruction, interactive exercises, real-world case studies, and discussions, participants will gain practical insights into facilitating Scrum events (Sprint Planning, Daily Scrum, Sprint Review, and Retrospective), coaching development teams, managing the Product Backlog, and effectively removing impediments to ensure successful project outcomes.</p>

    <h3>WHAT YOU’LL LEARN</h3>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">The program aims to equip individuals with the knowledge and skills necessary to foster team collaboration, promote continuous improvement, and drive Agile adoption within their organizations across diverse industries. This course is suitable for anyone involved in product delivery using Scrum, including aspiring Scrum Masters, Agile coaches, managers, and team members seeking to enhance their Agile capabilities.</p>

    <h3>MEET THE INSTRUCTORS</h3>
    <div class="instructors-icons">
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 John Doe</div>
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 Walter White</div>
      <div class="instructor-icon">😀 Jane Smith</div>
    </div>

    <h3>PMI</h3>
    <!-- <p>[...]</p> -->

    <button class="register-btn">Register</button>
  </section>

  <!-- Right Sidebar -->
  <aside class="course-right">
    <p>Length: <strong>2 months</strong></p>
    <p>Effort: <strong>Intermediate</strong></p>
    <p>Price: <strong>USD 499.00</strong></p>

    <h3>REVIEWS</h3>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>The Scrum Master certification training by SCRUMstudy was transformative for a career. The course content was comprehensive.</p>
</div>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>The Certified ScrumMaster (CSM) course taught by Eric Tucker was a very positive experience.</p>
</div>
    <div class="review-card">
  <ReviewIcon class="review-icon" />
  <p>This class was a relevant step in learning more about being a better scrum master and the journey in front of the scrum master.
  </p>
</div>

    <!-- <h3>WHAT YOU’LL LEARN</h3>
    <p>[...]</p>

    <h3>MEET THE INSTRUCTORS</h3>
    <p>[...]</p>

    <h3>PMI</h3>
    <p>[...]</p> -->
  </aside>
</main>

<style>
.course-detail-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 500px; 
  gap: 24px; 
  padding: 48px;
  background-color: #121212;
  color: white;
}

.course-left {
  padding-left: 48px; 
}

.course-left h2 {
  font-size: 26px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.course-left h3 {
  margin-top: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 20px;
}

.course-left p, .course-left li, .course-right p, .course-right li {
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-size: 16px;
}

.register-btn {
  background-color: #C4FEC7;
  color: black !important;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 24px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s;
  font-size: 12px;
}

.register-btn:hover {
  background-color: #a8e4aa;
}

.instructors-icons {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.instructor-icon {
  /* width: 52px; */
  height: 52px;
  background: #333;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 10%;
  padding: 5px;
  font-size: 24px;
}

.review-card {
  background: #333;
  height: 80px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  width: 80%;           /* 🚩 按比例缩小宽度 */
  margin-left: 0;       /* 🚩 左侧贴齐 */
  margin-right: auto;   /* 🚩 右侧留白缩进去 */
  padding: 12px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}
.review-icon {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
</style>
  <!-- Footer already in place -->

</body>
</html>